If youre not familiar with Doug Mastriano, a quick primer on the state senator turned gubernatorial candidate:
On November 5, 2020, he called for the resignation of Kathy Boockvar, the then secretary of the Pennsylvania Commonwealth, claiming that Pennsylvanians no longer feel secure in casting their vote?;
He wrote an email to a Department of Justice official, and asked that it be passed on to the then acting attorney general, in which he raised a litany of false and debunked claims of widespread election fraud in Pennsylvania, which Mastriano had previously aired at a November 25, 2020, hearing at a hotel in Gettysburg featuring Trump campaign lawyers Rudy Giuliani and Jenna Ellis,? as well as Trump himself via phone;
After Bidens PA win was official, he introduced a resolution to throw out the votes and just appoint Trump electors;
He used campaign funds to charter busses to the Stop the Steal? rally that preceded the violent riot;
Video footage shows that he and his wife took part in the...insurrection,? having crossed police lines and breaching the barricades set up at the Capitol;
On March 30, 2022, while campaigning for governor, he said: Im Doug Mastriano, and [if elected] I get to appoint the secretary of state whos delegated from me the power to make the corrections to elections, the voting logs and everything.
